==English==
===Etymology 1===
From {{inh|en|enm|yare}}, {{m|enm|ȝare}}, from {{inh|en|ang|ġearu||prepared, ready, prompt, equipped, complete, finished, yare}}, from {{inh|en|gmw-pro|*garu}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*garwaz||ready}}.
Cognate with {{cog|nl|gaar||done, well-cooked}}, {{cog|de|gar||done, well-cooked; wholly, at all}}, {{cog|is|görr}}, {{m|is|gerr||perfect}}.
